"""
Pegasus ROM Importer - NintenDeck Edition (Final)
- Consistent dark theme with Joy‑Con blue/red accents
- No white outlines, uniform scrollbars
- Fixed fullscreen flags for all emulators (Dolphin uses -b -e, no --fullscreen)
- Azahar supports Flatpak and apt
- Touch‑optimised file selector with light gray separators
- Metadata file: single collection header per platform, no duplication
"""

